use,  quite  frankly,  quite  often.  As  far  as  you  know,  there  hasn’t
been any sharing of information?

Dr. BELL. As far as I know, sir, there has not been.
Dr.  MARTYNY.  I  believe  there  has  been  some  work  by  Sandia
