Mr. Green.
Mr.  GREEN.  Thank  you,  Mr.  Chairman  and  Mr.  Ranking  Mem-
ber. I salute both of you and compliment you for having these hear-
ings,  and  quite  candidly,  for  being—allowing  me  to  be  a  part  of
